the village foreman and ran away.

786
01:02:07,960 --> 01:02:09,559
And he set his house on fire.

787
01:02:10,130 --> 01:02:13,000
I believe he was trying to erase
all of his traces.

788
01:02:13,869 --> 01:02:16,739
Due to his unsociable personality,
he didn't have any friends.

789
01:02:16,739 --> 01:02:18,110
When investigating
the village foreman's murder,

790
01:02:18,110 --> 01:02:19,909
the police couldn't get
a single photo of him.

791
01:02:21,079 --> 01:02:22,739
We'll need to get
a facial composite...

792
01:02:22,739 --> 01:02:24,079
based on
Mr. Noh Man Sik's description...

793
01:02:24,079 --> 01:02:25,380
since he knows
how Hyun Su looks now.

794
01:02:25,380 --> 01:02:26,880
This guy is a ghost.

795
01:02:27,880 --> 01:02:29,880
He didn't get an ID card either.

796
01:02:30,280 --> 01:02:32,619
He has no records
of using a credit card, a phone,

797
01:02:32,619 --> 01:02:35,190
or a transaction history. Nothing.

798
01:02:35,619 --> 01:02:37,460
How is he living?

799
01:02:37,460 --> 01:02:38,559
What about his family?

800
01:02:54,610 --> 01:02:55,739
I'll do it.

801
01:02:59,210 --> 01:03:01,119
Why are they talking about you
on TV?

802
01:03:01,449 --> 01:03:03,989
What are you doing these days?

803
01:03:05,849 --> 01:03:07,420
I'm looking into it.

804
01:03:07,420 --> 01:03:09,190
You should be lying low,

805
01:03:09,590 --> 01:03:11,190
so how dare you get involved
in a murder case?

806
01:03:11,630 --> 01:03:12,829
Have you gone insane?

807
01:03:13,059 --> 01:03:14,300
It has nothing to do with me.

808
01:03:15,599 --> 01:03:18,099
Had I known you were this sloppy,

809
01:03:18,269 --> 01:03:20,800
I wouldn't have chosen you
to be Baek Hee Seong.

810
01:03:59,110 --> 01:04:00,239
Hee Seong.

811
01:04:22,599 --> 01:04:24,269
(Baek Hee Seong)

812
01:04:24,269 --> 01:04:25,269
(Identity Card Application Form)

813
01:04:28,769 --> 01:04:29,769
(Baek Hee Seong, Do Hyun Su)

814
01:05:01,800 --> 01:05:06,170
(Flower of Evil)

815
01:05:06,269 --> 01:05:08,840
I told you! I warned you!

816
01:05:08,980 --> 01:05:10,809
The culprit was caught on CCTV...

817
01:05:10,909 --> 01:05:12,510
and left his blood
at the crime scene.

818
01:05:12,510 --> 01:05:13,750
This will get solved.

819
01:05:13,750 --> 01:05:16,650
Chasing after Do Hyun Su
won't lead them to Baek Hee Seong.

820
01:05:16,719 --> 01:05:18,719
Do Min Seok had a daughter.

821
01:05:18,719 --> 01:05:20,989
I've never seen Hyun Su
for the past 18 years.

822
01:05:20,989 --> 01:05:22,690
When will you believe me?

823
01:05:22,690 --> 01:05:23,889
You know who Ms. Bok Ja is, right?

824
01:05:23,889 --> 01:05:25,989
She has a photo of you
from five years ago.

825
01:05:26,489 --> 01:05:28,260
The police will visit her soon,

826
01:05:28,630 --> 01:05:29,800
and it'll be Detective Cha herself.

827
01:05:29,800 --> 01:05:31,230
Your wife is on her way
to catch you.

828
01:05:34,469 --> 01:05:35,570
Do Hyun Su!
